  "raw_block": "Unclean —Le 11:4;De 14:7.\nFound in deserted places —Eze 25:5.\nCharacterised by\n  The bunches on its back. —Isa 30:6.\n  Its docility. —Ge 24:11.\nThe dromedary a species of, remarkable for swiftness —Jer 2:23.\nAbounded in the east —1Ch 5:21;Isa 60:6.\nA part of patriarchal wealth —Ge 12:16;30:43;Job 1:3.\nKept in numbers by kings —1Ch 27:30.\nUsed for\n  Riding. —Ge 24:61.\n  Drawing chariots. —Isa 21:7.\n  Carrying burdens. —Ge 37:25;1Ki 10:2;2Ki 8:9.\n  Conveying posts and messengers. —Es 8:10.\n  War. —Jdj 7:12;1Sa 30:17.\nOf the rich adorned with chains —Jdj 8:21,26.\nFurniture of, alluded to —Ge 31:34.\nSubject to plagues —Ex 9:3;Zec 14:15.\nTreated with great care —Ge 24:31,32.\nEsteemed a valuable booty —1Ch 5:20,21;2Ch 14:15;Job 1:17;Jer 49:29,32.\nCoarse cloth made from its hair —Mt 3:4.\nReferred to in illustrations by Christ —Mt 19:24;23:24.",
